exercise.prompt:
Annotate this function so it only accepts two numbers and returns a number:

```ts
function add(a, b) {
  return a + b;
}
```

exercise.starterCode:
function add(a, b) {
  return a + b;
}
console.log(add(2, 3));

exercise.solution:
function add(a: number, b: number): number {
  return a + b;
}
console.log(add(2, 3)); // 5
